{"tid":408553,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有時係度諗，有冇啲人係棄養扮執到","createTime":"2017-09-21T10:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T08:12:58.000Z","uid":52068,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0979216a6236a4cd56a2902a475fa8b2cb8572ff","tid":408553,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:13:42.000Z","msg":"先講明，我唔係針對任何係度開post既巴絲打。我覺得願意領養、幫助動物既人真係好有善心。<br />\n<br />\n我知道每日都有寵物比人棄養，同時又有好多巴打無私付出幫緊啲動物揾新屋企。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但會唔會當中有一兩個人渣，自己棄養，再開post擺上網扮執到，話自己屋企唔養得，乜乜乜......<br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66af75b72cf1b88a775b0ea604df2105d960766d","tid":408553,"uid":76105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"有呀 我每朝都棄養隻狗，每晚再同自己講 領養番佢"},{"pid":"473fd12f4ab6b187ab414bd4c2b3c5cc6dd7e366","tid":408553,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"至少佢有幫隻寵物搵後路"},{"pid":"0ce36b7afa65e69b2e895e7caf2fcc671f9b2c8f","tid":408553,"uid":7555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有呀 我每朝都棄養隻狗，每晚再同自己講 領養番佢</blockquote><br />\n我老母都會咁做"},{"pid":"b3dd957b3eaa6857c45afc9e1fa80cb778c48a4d","tid":408553,"uid":83759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得實有呢種人"},{"pid":"0cc019c32e49941520cb98db1978179516b22755","tid":408553,"uid":130645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"你係咪已經對呢個世界冇晒信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a9a8ccbc1f91416d53b376c2ef0d8674d31059","tid":408553,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪已經對呢個世界冇晒信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n時不時會係度思考啲黑暗野"},{"pid":"1